content: CalmoAirPhoenix team is pleased to announce the Seed Sale of its $CAPH Token, it is started on 10th July 2022. Calmoairphoenix company is a new startup in the aerospace industry. The products of this company include 2-seater to 10-seater airplanes.More information on our website: https://calmoairphoenix.com/Seed-Sale RewardWe are glad to announce that $CAPH token seed-sale has Reward for who’s retweet it’s tweet.
